    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >―Features―</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique Puzzle Experience: Dive into an addictive and refreshing cube puzzle game!<br></li><li>Inventory Management: Strategically place items and build your unique setup!<br></li><li>Roguelite Elements: Experience new strategies and encounters with each run!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/42b82e3f000fb875294e085f02d3f017.poster.avif?t=1718431886\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/42b82e3f000fb875294e085f02d3f017.webm?t=1718431886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/42b82e3f000fb875294e085f02d3f017.mp4?t=1718431886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/4d563f184dbae480ec08cf0502812e03.poster.avif?t=1718431886\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/4d563f184dbae480ec08cf0502812e03.webm?t=1718431886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game features a 4×4×4 grid of mini-cubes. Swipe in any of the six directions, and all mini-cubes move accordingly. When three or more same-colored cubes align in the direction of movement, they merge and burst, triggering an attack! Combine multiple bursts at once for even greater damage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/5a8ad126aa9561a89469b929e42d20e3.avif?t=1718431886\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br><br>Sometimes, small companions called 'Sii' are born from the mini-cubes. These loyal allies automatically attack enemies but have short lifespans. Use items to extend their lifespans and maximize their effectiveness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/5158924f0dc724e62986316f763cf42d.poster.avif?t=1718431886\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/5158924f0dc724e62986316f763cf42d.webm?t=1718431886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/5158924f0dc724e62986316f763cf42d.mp4?t=1718431886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strategically place items and 'Sii' to advance with your unique strategies.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >―People Standing by 'Pathway'―</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019320/extras/763bdff8448a2f3c1e553cd2c7b38ff1.avif?t=1718431886\" width=600 height=273 /></span><br>On your journey, you may encounter the mysterious 'Pathway' Here, you will meet various characters. What is their connection to the 'CUBEN'...?<br><br>Get ready for an engaging puzzle adventure that combines strategy, excitement, and a bit of mystery!",
